The Board shall consist of the following seven members:
The Dean of the Virginia-Maryland Regional College of Veterinary Medicine, who shall serve as Chairman of the Board;
The Dean of the College of Agriculture and Natural Resources of the University of Maryland, College Park;
The Senior Vice President and Provost of the Virginia Polytechnic Institute and State University;
The Vice President and Provost of the University of Maryland, College Park;
The Executive Vice President and Chief Business Officer of the Virginia Polytechnic Institute and State University;
An appointee of the President of the Virginia Polytechnic Institute and State University; and
The Vice Chancellor for Administration and Finance of the University System of Maryland or the Vice Chancellor's successor.
